Package es.upm.pproject.parkingjam.parking_jam.model

Class GameSaver

java.lang.Object
es.upm.pproject.parkingjam.parking_jam.model.GameSaver
public class GameSaver extends Object
The GameSaver class is responsible for saving and loading the game state, including the level, score, and move history. It handles the creation and management of necessary files.
